etailer BWS just next door.", "In addition, customers can expect to see further improvements in the coming months with a brand new fit out of the", "produce and bakery departments.", "Woolworths Corio Store Manager, Matt Pickering, said the store has been a part of the local community since it opened", "a decade ago.", "\u201cWe are delighted our local Woolworths store has been upgraded, creating one of Australia\u2019s most modern", "supermarkets. The investment will deliver a supermarket local residents can continue to be proud of and support.", "\u201cThese improvements will enhance our customers\u2019 shopping experience as they pick up fresh Australian produce and", "meat, inspiring meal ideas, a wide choice of healthy options and a huge range of grocery items at great prices,\u201d Matt", "said.", "Customers can visit the revamped store during the usual trading hours of 7am to 10pm, seven days a week.", "The investment is part of a wider refurbishment program across Victoria, with around 10 supermarkets undergoing", "significant upgrades or extensions for the remainder of 2015.", "\u2010 Ends \u2010", "For further information please contact Woolworths Media Relations on ph (02) 8885 1033."], "bbox": [[0.092863, 0.214115, 0.814369, 0.019026], [0.047697, 0.252523, 0.904886, 0.01304], [0.047771, 0.268485, 0.42762, 0.01304], [0.047771, 0.300342, 0.907354, 0.01304], [0.047863, 0.316304, 0.9074169999999999, 0.01304], [0.047974, 0.332265, 0.072781, 0.01304], [0.047974, 0.364188, 0.907395, 0.01304], [0.047993, 0.380084, 0.393019, 0.01304], [0.04803, 0.412007, 0.7398309999999999, 0.01304], [0.048103, 0.44393, 0.907192, 0.01304], [0.047938, 0.459826, 0.25610900000000003, 0.01304], [0.047956, 0.491749, 0.904833, 0.01304], [0.047956, 0.507711, 0.10369699999999998, 0.01304], [0.047974, 0.539568, 0.9075460000000001, 0.01304], [0.048122, 0.55553, 0.862447, 0.01304], [0.048177, 0.587452, 0.907299, 0.01304], [0.048214, 0.603414, 0.9072830000000001, 0.01304], [0.048251, 0.61931